{"title":"Tiny Apidura Expedition Waist Belt Adds Jersey Pockets to Any Riding Kit","link":"https://bikerumor.com/tiny-apidura-expedition-waist-belt-adds-jersey-pockets-to-any-riding-kit/","date":1693916309000,"content":"<p><img width=\"1800\" height=\"1200\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/Apidura-Expedition-Waist-Belt-add-on-jersey-pockets_micro-hip-pack.jpg\" alt=\"Apidura Expedition Waist Belt add-on jersey pockets, minimalist hip pack\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/Apidura-Expedition-Waist-Belt-add-on-jersey-pockets_micro-hip-pack.jpg 1800w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/Apidura-Expedition-Waist-Belt-add-on-jersey-pockets_micro-hip-pack-297x198.jpg 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/Apidura-Expedition-Waist-Belt-add-on-jersey-pockets_micro-hip-pack-800x533.jpg 800w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/Apidura-Expedition-Waist-Belt-add-on-jersey-pockets_micro-hip-pack-120x80.jpg 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/Apidura-Expedition-Waist-Belt-add-on-jersey-pockets_micro-hip-pack-768x512.jpg 768w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/Apidura-Expedition-Waist-Belt-add-on-jersey-pockets_micro-hip-pack-1536x1024.jpg 1536w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/Apidura-Expedition-Waist-Belt-add-on-jersey-pockets_micro-hip-pack-720x480.jpg 720w\" /></p>\n<p>Apidura’s latest little Expedition Waist Belt is as simple a wearable storage solution as you could wish for. It’s the most minimalist hip pack imaginable. And it might just save your gravel, bikepacking, or even enduro mountain biking woes.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>So, if you’ve taken to riding in more relaxed fit clothes for greater comfort, modesty, or just better style on the bike, Apidura can bring back the classic benefits of 3 good ‘ol rear jersey pockets…</p>\n\n\n\n<h2>Apidura Expedition Waist Belt add-on jersey pockets</h2>\n\n\n\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/Apidura-Expedition-Waist-Belt-add-on-jersey-pockets-in-mini-hip-pack_filled.jpg\"><img width=\"900\" height=\"600\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/Apidura-Expedition-Waist-Belt-add-on-jersey-pockets-in-mini-hip-pack_filled.jpg\" alt=\"Apidura Expedition Waist Belt add-on jersey pockets, minimalist hip pack, loaded\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/Apidura-Expedition-Waist-Belt-add-on-jersey-pockets-in-mini-hip-pack_filled.jpg 900w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/Apidura-Expedition-Waist-Belt-add-on-jersey-pockets-in-mini-hip-pack_filled-297x198.jpg 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/Apidura-Expedition-Waist-Belt-add-on-jersey-pockets-in-mini-hip-pack_filled-800x533.jpg 800w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/Apidura-Expedition-Waist-Belt-add-on-jersey-pockets-in-mini-hip-pack_filled-120x80.jpg 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/Apidura-Expedition-Waist-Belt-add-on-jersey-pockets-in-mini-hip-pack_filled-768x512.jpg 768w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/Apidura-Expedition-Waist-Belt-add-on-jersey-pockets-in-mini-hip-pack_filled-720x480.jpg 720w\" /></a><figcaption><em>all c. Apidura</em></figcaption></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>Apidura specializes in helping you carry more on your bike rides. Their niche is lightweight, rackless bikepacking. The biggest part of that is probably gravel and off-road adventure riding, where trends are generally moving away from classic fitted lycra jerseys, and more in the direction of more comfortable, looser-fitting shirts and jerseys that also transition well off-the-bike. </p>\n\n\n\n<p>But ditching the dedicated cycling jersey for a tech tee often means losing all your pockets, too. Or bikepackers end up overstuffing what pockets they have, from shirts &amp; jerseys to bib shorts cargo pockets.</p>\n\n\n\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/Apidura-Expedition-Waist-Belt-add-on-jersey-pockets-in-mini-hip-pack_buckle.jpg\"><img width=\"900\" height=\"600\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/Apidura-Expedition-Waist-Belt-add-on-jersey-pockets-in-mini-hip-pack_buckle.jpg\" alt=\"Apidura Expedition Waist Belt add-on jersey pockets, minimalist hip pack, buckle and belt\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/Apidura-Expedition-Waist-Belt-add-on-jersey-pockets-in-mini-hip-pack_buckle.jpg 900w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/Apidura-Expedition-Waist-Belt-add-on-jersey-pockets-in-mini-hip-pack_buckle-297x198.jpg 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/Apidura-Expedition-Waist-Belt-add-on-jersey-pockets-in-mini-hip-pack_buckle-800x533.jpg 800w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/Apidura-Expedition-Waist-Belt-add-on-jersey-pockets-in-mini-hip-pack_buckle-120x80.jpg 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/Apidura-Expedition-Waist-Belt-add-on-jersey-pockets-in-mini-hip-pack_buckle-768x512.jpg 768w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/Apidura-Expedition-Waist-Belt-add-on-jersey-pockets-in-mini-hip-pack_buckle-720x480.jpg 720w\" /></a></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>So, enter a set of strap-on jersey pockets, with a simple adjustable belt &amp; buckle. </p>\n\n\n\n<p>Or as Apidura calls it, the Expedition Waist Belt.</p>\n\n\n\n<h3>Tech details</h3>\n\n\n\n<figure>\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/Apidura-Expedition-Waist-Belt-add-on-jersey-pockets-in-mini-hip-pack_rear.jpg\"><img width=\"1200\" height=\"1000\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/Apidura-Expedition-Waist-Belt-add-on-jersey-pockets-in-mini-hip-pack_rear.jpg\" alt=\"Apidura Expedition Waist Belt add-on jersey pockets, minimalist hip pack, rear\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/Apidura-Expedition-Waist-Belt-add-on-jersey-pockets-in-mini-hip-pack_rear.jpg 1200w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/Apidura-Expedition-Waist-Belt-add-on-jersey-pockets-in-mini-hip-pack_rear-297x248.jpg 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/Apidura-Expedition-Waist-Belt-add-on-jersey-pockets-in-mini-hip-pack_rear-800x667.jpg 800w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/Apidura-Expedition-Waist-Belt-add-on-jersey-pockets-in-mini-hip-pack_rear-120x100.jpg 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/Apidura-Expedition-Waist-Belt-add-on-jersey-pockets-in-mini-hip-pack_rear-768x640.jpg 768w\" /></a></figure>\n\n\n\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/Apidura-Expedition-Waist-Belt-add-on-jersey-pockets-in-mini-hip-pack_front.jpg\"><img width=\"1200\" height=\"1000\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/Apidura-Expedition-Waist-Belt-add-on-jersey-pockets-in-mini-hip-pack_front.jpg\" alt=\"Apidura Expedition Waist Belt add-on jersey pockets, minimalist hip pack, front\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/Apidura-Expedition-Waist-Belt-add-on-jersey-pockets-in-mini-hip-pack_front.jpg 1200w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/Apidura-Expedition-Waist-Belt-add-on-jersey-pockets-in-mini-hip-pack_front-297x248.jpg 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/Apidura-Expedition-Waist-Belt-add-on-jersey-pockets-in-mini-hip-pack_front-800x667.jpg 800w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/Apidura-Expedition-Waist-Belt-add-on-jersey-pockets-in-mini-hip-pack_front-120x100.jpg 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/Apidura-Expedition-Waist-Belt-add-on-jersey-pockets-in-mini-hip-pack_front-768x640.jpg 768w\" /></a></figure>\n</figure>\n\n\n\n<p>The breathable 4-way-stretch padded mesh Apidura Expedition Waist Belt offers 1L of combined storage in 3 jersey-style pockets. Two smaller side hip pockets angle slightly forward, compared to the larger full-height ~13cm tall center pocket. None get any secure closure (like a zip or velcro), instead relying on the stretchy fabric to keep your gear in place.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Claimed weight for the on-bike anatomically cut waist belt is just 70g for S/M or 75g for L/XL</p>\n\n\n\n<h3>Apidura Expedition Waist Belt – Pricing, Options &amp; Availability</h3>\n\n\n\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/Apidura-Expedition-Waist-Belt-add-on-jersey-pockets-in-mini-hip-pack_over-bib-shorts.jpg\"><img width=\"1500\" height=\"900\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/Apidura-Expedition-Waist-Belt-add-on-jersey-pockets-in-mini-hip-pack_over-bib-shorts.jpg\" alt=\"Apidura Expedition Waist Belt add-on jersey pockets, minimalist hip pack, over bib shorts\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/Apidura-Expedition-Waist-Belt-add-on-jersey-pockets-in-mini-hip-pack_over-bib-shorts.jpg 1500w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/Apidura-Expedition-Waist-Belt-add-on-jersey-pockets-in-mini-hip-pack_over-bib-shorts-297x178.jpg 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/Apidura-Expedition-Waist-Belt-add-on-jersey-pockets-in-mini-hip-pack_over-bib-shorts-800x480.jpg 800w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/Apidura-Expedition-Waist-Belt-add-on-jersey-pockets-in-mini-hip-pack_over-bib-shorts-120x72.jpg 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/Apidura-Expedition-Waist-Belt-add-on-jersey-pockets-in-mini-hip-pack_over-bib-shorts-768x461.jpg 768w\" /></a></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>The belt comes in two sizes S/M to fit 75-95cm (29.5-37″) or L/XL to fit 90-105cm (35-41″) circumferences. Keep in mind then, that’s not your waist size necessarily. You need to measure overtop of whatever you want to wear under the waist belt – after all, maybe that’s a pair of bib shorts, just some regular shorts, or several more layers of clothing. You decide.</p>\n\n\n\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/Apidura-Expedition-Waist-Belt-add-on-jersey-pockets-in-mini-hip-pack_with-stuff.jpg\"><img width=\"1500\" height=\"800\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/Apidura-Expedition-Waist-Belt-add-on-jersey-pockets-in-mini-hip-pack_with-stuff.jpg\" alt=\"Apidura Expedition Waist Belt add-on jersey pockets, minimalist hip pack, loaded\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/Apidura-Expedition-Waist-Belt-add-on-jersey-pockets-in-mini-hip-pack_with-stuff.jpg 1500w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/Apidura-Expedition-Waist-Belt-add-on-jersey-pockets-in-mini-hip-pack_with-stuff-297x158.jpg 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/Apidura-Expedition-Waist-Belt-add-on-jersey-pockets-in-mini-hip-pack_with-stuff-800x427.jpg 800w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/Apidura-Expedition-Waist-Belt-add-on-jersey-pockets-in-mini-hip-pack_with-stuff-120x64.jpg 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/Apidura-Expedition-Waist-Belt-add-on-jersey-pockets-in-mini-hip-pack_with-stuff-768x410.jpg 768w\" /></a></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>It may be simple and light, but the Apidura Expedition Waist Belt still sells for $49 / 38 / 44€ – available from today. Sure, that’s not exactly cheap, but it does give any shirt or jersey classic pockets again.</p>\n\n\n\n<p><em><a href=\"https://www.apidura.com/\" target=\"_blank\">Apidura.com</a></em></p>\n<p>The post <a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/tiny-apidura-expedition-waist-belt-adds-jersey-pockets-to-any-riding-kit/\">Tiny Apidura Expedition Waist Belt Adds Jersey Pockets to Any Riding Kit</a> appeared first on <a href=\"https://bikerumor.com\">Bikerumor</a>.</p>","author":"Cory Benson","siteTitle":"Bikerumor","siteHash":"49f427af0a926f4232eb837006841d7242e153e3afbb590f32e4b104ea3e2718","entryHash":"a371cecffacf7abc12dcba0b3e008f8329bf15f964485e7c32abe73c5653829a","category":"Cycling"}